00:29:51.276 --> 00:29:55.940
on the union of the two loops
where you delete the common

00:29:55.940 --> 00:29:56.690
edge.
 

00:29:56.690 --> 00:29:58.358
You have to understand this.
 

00:29:58.358 --> 00:30:00.980
I will not leave any child
behind.

00:30:00.980 --> 00:30:03.108
You have to know why this is
