00:36:04.320 --> 00:36:06.329
Now you might say,
"Why don't you go a little

00:36:06.329 --> 00:36:06.739
further?
 

00:36:06.739 --> 00:36:09.110
Kill the B also."
 

00:36:09.110 --> 00:36:09.789
You can try that.
 

00:36:09.789 --> 00:36:12.806
If you kill the B,
