00:36:35.199 --> 00:36:39.019
I have to take a cube, right?
 

00:36:39.019 --> 00:36:41.000
Let me take the cube.
 

00:36:41.000 --> 00:36:43.326
It's infinitesimal,
but I'm just keeping it near

00:36:43.326 --> 00:36:43.969
